main event: A witness in Nome, Alaska reported seeing a blurred, brilliant white oval object that disappeared by diminishing after one minute of observation.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about one minute., The object was described as oval, white, and brilliant., It disappeared by dimming after being observed., There were additional reports from the area indicating the presence of objects in orbit., The witness had not been reported by the Ground Observer Corps.
witness description: The witness was described as reliable and had not been in trouble of this nature before.
